lead_paragraph: England lock Joe Launchbury will miss the tests against Argentina and Australia after being handed a two-week ban by a disciplinary committee for kicking an opponent in Saturday's win over Fiji.

headline.print_headline: England's Launchbury Gets Two-Week Ban, Misses Two Games
